CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 30, 1947, pg. 10, reads: "Pittsburgh Weddings - Repeating marriage vows recently where the couples pictured above... third: Mr. and Mrs. Edward Jackson... - All photos by Harris." Portion of accompanying article reads: "Perry - Jackson. Miss Evelyn Perry [illegible]... daughter of Mr. and Mrs... [il.] of Elizabeth, Pa... Edward Jackson... Mrs. R. K.... following..."
TitMainTitle: Groom Edward Jackson and bride Evelyn Perry posed behind three tiered wedding cake in interior with floral wallpaper and lace curtains
